oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Maintaining the Integrity of the Accredited Veterinarian System
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Hawkins, Bert W.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: accredited veterinarian system
accredited veterinarians
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: It is certainly a pleasure to be with you today to share my thoughts on a subject of vital importance: maintaining the integrity of the accredited veterinarian system. I am talking here about a system that is directly connected to international confidence in our cattle and other livestock exports, as well as confidence among states.
